    title: 'Computers + Software',
    items: [
      'Intel i7 2600K (3.4 GHz x8)', '16gb RAM', '1 TB SysHD', '1 TB SamplesHD', '2 TB AudioHD (x2)',
      'Pro tools 10', 'Various UA & Slate Plugins', "Various synths & add'l plugs",
